{
  "_id": "kWkIvI7T6XFbABGiW9Xwi5",
  "body": [
    {
      "_key": "93953d3e-1c43-49d7-a6e0-719f90dbcb1a",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "13e96a8f-1ca1-43ae-8351-af71ac8848b2",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "医療現場で患者さんのケアに携わる仕事として、「看護助手」と「介護職員初任者研修」という言葉を耳にすることがあるでしょう。どちらも身体介助などを行うため、混同されがちですが、その役割や働く場所、求められる資格には明確な違いがあります。"
        },
        {
          "_key": "33588efa-8616-47a3-a5a9-6e24c0efc769",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "\n"
        },
        {
          "_key": "c4e3c451-f1ff-4b17-9c9b-84c91d5fa2c9",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "_key": "22ea6b38-b064-4b74-89ae-c71856967df0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "\n"
        },
        {
          "_key": "f76ea8f9-f97f-4834-baad-94ec060122ed",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "この記事では、看護助手と介護職員初任者研修の違いを徹底的に比較し、それぞれの職種がどんな人に向いているかを解説します。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-366ad440-63f5-4c3c-b902-96abf9be42e9",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-3cba8fef-aec4-414a-a898-de39703fdc56",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-68bae435-af2c-4dad-bc08-da610aae374b",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-d4af4724-ed83-4a32-971f-10084fcea0b1"
          ],
          "text": "日本看護協会 看護補助者の離職状況レポート"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-d4af4724-ed83-4a32-971f-10084fcea0b1",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.nurse.or.jp/home/assets/20231005_nl01.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "261519af-5651-4d5d-b86e-bdab8cf8d7c9",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e67d7552-3ac5-46c1-9159-0fffa816ce84",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "492645ad-149c-4d21-9b37-21941137de1b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "ba7c8a56-913f-4400-bb47-97417cd2d341-4e09fd78-321d-4425-9b7f-3909c7956838",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "資格"
        },
        {
          "_key": "ba7c8a56-913f-4400-bb47-97417cd2d341-dc26bfe0-35d2-480e-b884-7a98a945780c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 必須の資格はありません。無資格・未経験からでも働くことができます。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "4b9fe41a-fd7d-417c-973c-d645353c4596",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "2562fac9-ed54-4842-aa9a-97b16bd337bb-5e5ac924-710e-4bca-a61d-aad2d8478d2a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "業務範囲"
        },
        {
          "_key": "2562fac9-ed54-4842-aa9a-97b16bd337bb-a6162bae-33ed-42b1-8a72-799ed37b7bce",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 看護師の指示のもと、患者さんの身の回りのお世話（食事、入浴、排泄介助など）や環境整備、看護師の補助業務（医療器具の準備、メッセンジャー業務など）を行います。"
        },
        {
          "_key": "2562fac9-ed54-4842-aa9a-97b16bd337bb-b2b12ec7-24f5-416f-8967-dbf96c40af2b",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "医療行為は一切できません。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "a26eecca-9efe-4021-b2a9-2e5c51ac7783",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "a44813c5-04af-4e6c-b401-f8f2c77530dc-4d23755d-a184-4750-94fd-2059d2f10d03",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "働く場所"
        },
        {
          "_key": "a44813c5-04af-4e6c-b401-f8f2c77530dc-cfd81620-66e8-4417-8e25-656c958d08c4",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 主に病院の病棟や外来、クリニックなど、医療機関が中心です。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-14b6b983-caf0-45d4-88d2-b875aad290d3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-2f707b40-c530-40c3-801c-b53db33899a0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "上記の点に注意しながら、無理なく取り組んでいきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "61a5e29c-dc26-4bf1-8bf2-604e5a1ff400",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "61856e56-994b-4978-9f73-2ca38d800974",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "介護職員初任者研修"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "a8d64504-415b-4481-afa4-d6423dd3cacc",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "09af4805-1a0e-47cd-af7d-9325b756f4cc-1aa5e55b-ded4-444e-916c-f898e2fd8e66",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "資格"
        },
        {
          "_key": "09af4805-1a0e-47cd-af7d-9325b756f4cc-7e1ba75b-a8a1-4e80-b2ed-c339a3df2751",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 介護に関する基本的な知識と技術を習得したことを証明する公的な資格です。約130時間の研修（座学と実技）を修了することで取得できます。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "affiliate-cta-ee2b1a11-f0e2-451e-954c-b0db3bf8d0f4",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "affiliate-cta-span-c94d275a-e264-418f-93a0-a68c988d02a1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "「介護職員初任者研修」で感じた課題を整理するときはかいご畑に相談して条件やサポート体制を具体化してみてください。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "c2bb7916-9c62-4cb7-9bdf-b11395423210",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "deac3d5a-9a17-4758-8602-82fe7e577812-aec08265-f67a-48d6-aaba-29864c6ccefa",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "業務範囲"
        },
        {
          "_key": "deac3d5a-9a17-4758-8602-82fe7e577812-af52e51d-b03e-4d06-813a-06003378cb11",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 利用者さんの身体介護（食事、入浴、排泄介助など）や生活援助（掃除、洗濯、買い物など）を行います。"
        },
        {
          "_key": "deac3d5a-9a17-4758-8602-82fe7e577812-b5295e09-afb1-4370-b691-1dbb6b136f86",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "医療行為はできませんが、介護の専門家として自らの判断でケアを行うことができます。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "9a2d070b-0583-4c29-a746-ad7e5cc36047",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "be0dfb4c-fc8d-432e-8b23-ad4c9de8d459-6aed12c4-22da-4d34-b4f9-0c0d65b54f8a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "働く場所"
        },
        {
          "_key": "be0dfb4c-fc8d-432e-8b23-ad4c9de8d459-f8ed0b14-4383-4779-88dd-d7369db4e494",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 特別養護老人ホーム、介護老人保健施設、デイサービス、訪問介護事業所など、介護施設が中心です。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-faf553de-1759-47a4-98bf-e5d8bb922ce5",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-d556f437-8ea0-46e9-a253-9ef9c733388d",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "これらを参考に、自分に合った方法を見つけてください。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "1a5ec6c7-daad-45a5-a8a5-bff66fdfaf2d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "774b20fe-5d45-4e29-a8cd-ca6a154f8df3",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "2. 働く場所と対象者の違い"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "884278e0-8324-48b0-8f6e-7b8d42a01059",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "6b4b764d-8f4a-47ba-974a-191949331c29",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "2af62281-a21f-43e4-9933-04dcfe99ad7a",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "2dee184c-502a-4d61-af7e-c3a7705d0286-471c1886-d811-481a-8fa9-93ffb899226a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "働く場所"
        },
        {
          "_key": "2dee184c-502a-4d61-af7e-c3a7705d0286-5448182f-8101-4dd3-bef8-c67f1b7094ea",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 病院やクリニックといった「医療機関」がメインです。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "a7e40b96-2a12-4e9f-8cbb-28ff8add3e8f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "8f1dbb8b-d450-441a-a453-dca9858044b4-f98058b6-dcb3-419c-b94a-60c849e9e993",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "対象者"
        },
        {
          "_key": "8f1dbb8b-d450-441a-a453-dca9858044b4-352ee745-2725-4c9f-8dbf-e15c351bb475",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 病気や怪我で治療を受けている「患者さん」が主な対象です。治療の補助という側面が強いです。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "followup-aa89824d-6be4-48ad-ba71-99b7240f7a7e",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "text-3bc80bae-11db-403d-a8c2-2d7b12c8796e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "上記の点に注意しながら、無理なく取り組んでいきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "reference-f22c9d01-f4b5-473a-a532-82202c507c2e",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-label-cf01c072-9aa4-44a0-a925-9dfdd16e5c39",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: "
        },
        {
          "_key": "reference-span-link-ed9c21ff-7c3e-48be-a1b0-34117d8a18dc",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-f47cd5b7-13f1-4758-807e-1c089dcf6f2e"
          ],
          "text": "日本看護協会 看護サービス提供体制のあり方"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-f47cd5b7-13f1-4758-807e-1c089dcf6f2e",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.nurse.or.jp/home/publication/pdf/guideline/way_of_nursing_service.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "e7f0957b-f000-4b7e-8d75-b6e672d19f32",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "45360483-1e2f-4dda-b017-f8d9411173ef",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "介護職員初任者研修"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "b699d116-9cc7-43ae-96a8-195b563382d2",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "3565a801-dfc2-4874-ad23-e362e8f94f7c-268f23aa-a0e3-449e-9547-b9900e648ce0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "働く場所"
        },
        {
          "_key": "3565a801-dfc2-4874-ad23-e362e8f94f7c-20052a1d-fc03-46e1-aca3-7b92522e20aa",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 介護施設や在宅介護サービスを提供する「介護事業所」がメインです。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "4de82239-dee3-4153-96d4-372205ff05a0",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e301eb0b-dc7b-4fd7-a8e4-7cda2e1dfc51-147f9db3-bb1b-482d-91c9-5ede51401235",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "対象者"
        },
        {
          "_key": "e301eb0b-dc7b-4fd7-a8e4-7cda2e1dfc51-38040ffc-c1fd-4c73-9c55-a1f438e12a8a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 高齢者や障がい者など、日常生活に支援が必要な「利用者さん」が主な対象です。生活の質の向上を目的とした支援が中心です。"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "listItem": "bullet",
      "markDefs": []
    },
    {
      "_key": "section-closing-fa7919a8-c848-4e5e-81a0-6b9168977a6e",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "section-closing-span-1acdebbf-536d-44ba-a889-2990786caf59",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "2. 働く場所と対象者の違いでは、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "5295fb70-1b6d-40ef-b802-d516890585a0",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "d5466509-a4db-4e66-83ca-a2d37807d912",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "3. キャリアパスの違い"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "8dff080d-4c68-4203-8226-1ad1b20c6a91",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "f8af0184-78bf-42fa-a2ae-79735208c7cf",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "6d664ec9-c18f-4152-bb04-16180e93e6ab",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "cff08dac-8a8e-4a9c-a7bd-f643376fadc0",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手として経験を積んだ後、さらに専門性を高めたい場合は、看護師や准看護師の資格取得を目指したり、介護福祉士などの介護系資格を取得して介護分野へキャリアチェンジしたりする道があります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "0a9bfbae-208c-4691-ac2a-295c7f208b7b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "e1ee5bd8-57de-4fff-8547-1918f063627e",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "介護職員初任者研修"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "f479f570-7dea-4870-821e-8f2436abf5c9",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "f2e4f87d-3b32-4874-9236-5516a89c26ae",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "介護職員初任者研修は、介護分野でのキャリアの第一歩となる資格です。この後、「実務者研修」を経て、介護分野唯一の国家資格である「介護福祉士」を目指すのが一般的なキャリアパスです。さらに経験を積めば、「ケアマネージャー（介護支援専門員）」への道も開かれます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d2d29f5c-996c-4c45-80f6-9d5cb78f30af",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "3fdf7fd4-5906-46f2-98b9-c2af9695c6b8",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "どちらの仕事が向いている？"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "47d799f2-b539-42a6-8719-33c402e5f564",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "40c79742-ea76-4b27-98fe-58805b84d7a8",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "看護助手が向いている人"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "a107f676-ccd6-4ed8-8670-42fe7d588c8e",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "9bbe926b-a4a5-438a-b2ab-927f304b1311-94c6e854-470a-405b-91ef-50c7db4b4fef",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "医療現場で働きたい人"
        },
        {
